query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(q tq s) */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 5
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('sharepoint')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('2007',
'content-type',
'csom',
'custom-list',
'designer-workflow',
'infopath',
'jquery',
'office-365',
'permissions',
'rest',
'sharepoint-addin');
